transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello, Jain Auto Equipments, hello, Jain Auto Equipments company se baat ho rahi hai?
Executive: Haan ji.
Customer: Sir, Shyam ji se baat ho jayegi? Main Indiamart.com ke Noida head office se Satish Tiwari bol raha tha.
Executive: Ah, nahi aap galat abhi maine utha liya aap wapas se call kijiye to wo uthayenge. Dono ka kya same matlab aisa hai main ya unme se ek jana uthata Indiamart ki call.
Customer: Aisa nahi but India ke sare jana jawab dene jawab dene wo wohi dete hain Indiamart ke liye aisa koi bhi kaam hota hai vaisa wohi karte hain wohi handle karte hain.
Executive: Barabar.
Customer: Okay, okay.
